report_template:
## Outcome resume change report

**Target role:** {{target_role}}
**JD keywords used (truthful only):** {{keywords_used}}
**Pages constraint:** {{max_pages}}

### Summary of changes
- Rewrote {{rewritten_bullets}} bullets to lead with outcomes
- Quantified {{quantified_bullets}} bullets; inserted {{placeholders_count}} placeholders for missing metrics
- Removed banned phrases: {{banned_hits}}
- Consolidated skills: {{skills_actions}}
- Reordered sections to: {{section_order}}

### Before and after excerpts
{{#each examples}}
- **Location:** {{this.location}}
  - Before: {{this.before}}
  - After: {{this.after}}
  - Rationale: {{this.why}}
{{/each}}

### Items requiring your review
{{#if review_flags.length}}
{{#each review_flags}}- **{{this.severity | upper}}** — {{this.location}}: {{this.issue}}. Suggested fix: {{this.suggested_fix}}
{{/each}}
{{else}}- None
{{/if}}

### Placeholders to replace
{{#if placeholders.length}}
{{#each placeholders}}- {{this.location}} → {{this.prompt}}
{{/each}}
{{else}}- None
{{/if}}

### ATS alignment (truthful)
- Keywords mapped: {{keywords_used}}
- Not used (irrelevant or unsubstantiated): {{keywords_ignored}}

### Final checklist
{{#each qa_results}}- {{this.item}}: {{this.status}}
{{/each}}
